Unique Features
* Watch Exhibition Đ Get notified when stall bookings open. 
* Compare Exhibitions Đ Compare visitor count, exhibitors, industries, and pricing. 
* Favorite Exhibitions Đ Save exhibitions to a wishlist. 
* Recently Viewed Đ Quickly revisit exhibitions. 
* Recommended Based on Your Industry Đ Personalized suggestions using AI. 
* Repeat Exhibitors Đ See which companies have participated in previous editions. 
* Live Stall Availability Đ Stall colors update instantly as bookings happen. 
This approach makes the application similar to BookMyShow for exhibitions on the home page, while providing a powerful interactive stall booking and exhibition management platform once users enter an exhibition. It serves organizers, exhibitors, and visitors from a single application.

